column79: Probably something about how people should work together for mutual benefit instead of just for themselves, but that some people won't do it, even when it makes for sense for everyone, because they are having trouble trusting. Giving 30 DKK is better for everyone, because not only just everyone get more money - you also show trust in eachother to do the same thing again instead of running scams on eachother.
